thread.title: Treasury to Sell $163 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $163 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $163 billion in securities next week, comprising $73 billion in new debt and $90 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $48 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Feb. 8, 2018, maturing Aug. 9, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PU7.
